即使 明天 下雨 ， 我 也 要 去 学校 。 > 即使 …，… 也 …Even if , Even though.The conjunction phrase‘even if’is used to say that if something is the case or not , the result is the same.The former clause is a supposition , and ‘ yě ’ is placed between the subject and verb in the latter one.
